Text replacement plugin for Pidgin, with regex support. Can be used to
linkify user-defined strings in IM messages.

Original version by Sadrul Habib Chowdhury <sadrul@pidgin.im>
downloaded from http://pidgin.im/~sadrul/pp/pl/replaceX.pl

advanced-replaceX.pl enhancements by Stefan Gipper <support@coder-world.de>
downloaded from
http://advanced-replacex-perl-pidgin.googlecode.com/files/advanced-replacex.pl
